desc: Diller Greenhouses is a local, family-owned and operated greenhouse located in Council Bluffs, Iowa. For three generations we have offered our customers quality plants, great selection and customer service.

layout.text: Greenhouses are closed for the season. Opening again mid April 2023
LOCALLY GROWN & FAMILY OWNED Feel good knowing you’re supporting a local family business whose three generations have served the Council Bluffs + Omaha metro area for almost 100 years.
